text: Jin Jian (; ; born 9 March 1994) is a Chinese bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of China Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
